## Task 4 — Database and Table Statements

### Database commands

```sql
-- Create a new database
CREATE DATABASE thm_bookmarket_db;

-- List all databases
SHOW DATABASES;

-- Switch to a database
USE thm_bookmarket_db;

-- Delete a database (irreversible)
DROP DATABASE database_name;
```

### Table commands

```sql
-- Create a table with defined columns and data types
CREATE TABLE book_inventory (
    book_id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    book_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    publication_date DATE
);

-- List all tables in the active database
SHOW TABLES;

-- View the structure of a table
DESCRIBE book_inventory;

-- Add a new column to an existing table
ALTER TABLE book_inventory ADD page_count INT;

-- Delete a table (irreversible)
DROP TABLE table_name;
```

