## Commands Reference

| Command | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `CREATE DATABASE x` | Create a new database |
| `SHOW DATABASES` | List all databases |
| `USE x` | Switch active database |
| `DROP DATABASE x` | Delete a database |
| `CREATE TABLE x (...)` | Create a table |
| `SHOW TABLES` | List tables in active DB |
| `DESCRIBE x` | Show table structure |
| `ALTER TABLE x ADD col type` | Add a column |
| `DROP TABLE x` | Delete a table |
| `INSERT INTO x (...) VALUES (...)` | Add a record |
| `SELECT * FROM x` | Read all records |
| `UPDATE x SET col=val WHERE ...` | Modify a record |
| `DELETE FROM x WHERE ...` | Remove a record |
| `SELECT DISTINCT col FROM x` | Unique values only |
| `GROUP BY col` | Group rows |
| `ORDER BY col ASC/DESC` | Sort results |
| `HAVING condition` | Filter after grouping |
| `LIMIT n` | Cap number of results |
